title: Bubba the Love Sponge All Audio CDs
description:
Part of my own collection and some others from other places.

Includes every audio CD Bubba the Love Sponge has released. Essentially it is the K5 Anthology.

Included 11 .ISOs:
Best of Bucs Bits, Masturbation CD, Ned Only 2
Bubba Wanna Corndog Discs 1 & 2
Mansons Greatest Hits and Neds Fucking Classics
Morning Domination Discs 1 & 2
Ned Only 1 & I'm A Big Fat Greasy Bitch
On the Chip Discs 1 & 2
Public Enema #1 Discs 1 & 2
Raw & Uncensored Discs 1 & 2
The Fat and the Furious Discs 1 & 2
The Kabuki Project & Bubba's Boys With the Bass
The Todd Clem Project Discs 1 & 2

Paired them as I got them. Split everything up figuring that some people would only need parts.

Enjoy. 
Vote for Brookie!
